fullText: The show finds its groove when it stops trying so hard to be clever and lets the pop anthems do their work, creating moments of genuine emotional connection amid the fairy-tale chaos.
dtliExcerpt: In any case, “Once Upon a One More Time” is a dizzy but enjoyable goof, similar in many ways to “& Juliet.”
